    • Method Detail

      • begin

        private void begin()
            throws java.io.IOException
        Beginning of the chunked upload. If the request parameters for this method are supplied, chunked upload is started. The main purpose of this method is to obtain a session identifier for further data upload. This request uploads maximum of one single chunk of data.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If something fails.

      • exec
